  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/2b5447e3de2d9300ac7369f892c35443.webp?t=1769630387\" width=430 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kingdom of Peace</strong> is an addictive adventure game <strong>created by one person, </strong>set in a brutal and at the same time beautiful medieval world. Take on the role of Racław, a hero forced to escape from the cruelty of war, to find shelter and start a new life in a more peaceful land. Your journey is a story of courage, sacrifice and the fight to survive in a harsh reality. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛡️ <strong>An epic adventure in two lands</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience Racław's dramatic journey through two medieval lands. Fleeing from the war, the hero finds himself in a new kingdom, where he will have to build a new life and deal with the everyday challenges of being the manager of his own settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/93bdf89c3587c44a7827094662c00824.avif?t=1769630387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras_big/93bdf89c3587c44a7827094662c00824.avif?t=1769630387 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Construction and development of the settlement</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After reaching the new land, Racław will have the chance to found his own settlement. Build houses, mills, bakeries and other structures that will help create a self-sustaining community. Manage resources, take care of the inhabitants and prepare the settlement for unforeseen difficulties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/737f493ae65745cafbc759e31ffe7f7f.avif?t=1769630387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras_big/737f493ae65745cafbc759e31ffe7f7f.avif?t=1769630387 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍞 <strong>Realistic needs and survival</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunger and thirst will be a daily challenge. Search for food, water and shelter while protecting yourself and others from the dangers of life in the medieval world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/267d7f99e43371d38b314414f08e4cd6.avif?t=1769630387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras_big/267d7f99e43371d38b314414f08e4cd6.avif?t=1769630387 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌄 <strong>Discover the beauty and brutality of the medieval world</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore diverse landscapes, from picturesque villages and peaceful fields to dangerous forests and ruined settlements that provide a hiding place for sinister bandits. Each place hides its secrets and stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/2083f0808300235970a20f38eaed1e91.avif?t=1769630387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras_big/2083f0808300235970a20f38eaed1e91.avif?t=1769630387 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭 <strong>Rich plot</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about Racław's history and his fight for a better tomorrow. Meet colorful characters, solve problems and discover how the war affected people in both kingdoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/5b42a5e14f67ab77c2c0ec2b64c46fd0.avif?t=1769630387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras_big/5b42a5e14f67ab77c2c0ec2b64c46fd0.avif?t=1769630387 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Kingdom of Peace</strong> is the story of a man facing the cruelty of war and trying to build a future in a world full of challenges. Will Racław find peace and a place to call home? <strong>See for yourself ;)</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/2b5447e3de2d9300ac7369f892c35443.webp?t=1769630387\" width=430 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kingdom of Peace</strong> is an addictive adventure game <strong>created by one person, </strong>set in a brutal and at the same time beautiful medieval world. Take on the role of Racław, a hero forced to escape from the cruelty of war, to find shelter and start a new life in a more peaceful land. Your journey is a story of courage, sacrifice and the fight to survive in a harsh reality. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛡️ <strong>An epic adventure in two lands</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience Racław's dramatic journey through two medieval lands. Fleeing from the war, the hero finds himself in a new kingdom, where he will have to build a new life and deal with the everyday challenges of being the manager of his own settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/93bdf89c3587c44a7827094662c00824.avif?t=1769630387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras_big/93bdf89c3587c44a7827094662c00824.avif?t=1769630387 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Construction and development of the settlement</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After reaching the new land, Racław will have the chance to found his own settlement. Build houses, mills, bakeries and other structures that will help create a self-sustaining community. Manage resources, take care of the inhabitants and prepare the settlement for unforeseen difficulties.<