" >Learn about Racław's history and his fight for a better tomorrow. Meet colorful characters, solve problems and discover how the war affected people in both kingdoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras/5b42a5e14f67ab77c2c0ec2b64c46fd0.avif?t=1769630387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904920/extras_big/5b42a5e14f67ab77c2c0ec2b64c46fd0.avif?t=1769630387 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Kingdom of Peace</strong> is the story of a man facing the cruelty of war and trying to build a future in a world full of challenges. Will Racław find peace and a place to call home? <strong>See for yourself ;)</strong></p>",
